    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找一块可以建造家园的土地。一开始你只是普通的农夫或猎人，但当你获得更多经验、好好学习和磨练技能后，你就可以成为这座繁荣城镇的首领。设计、建造并改善你的房屋——从蓬户柴门到广阔的农场。说服人们加入你的村庄。寻找真爱，组建家庭，确保王朝的延续。您可以独自或与朋友在合作模式中组队，一起探索美丽而残酷的中世纪世界。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/9a9879825abd6312cc29814f12fc2f82.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/d9568a5238bc44eef01a78f762ed3c7e.poster.avif?t=1770646795\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/d9568a5238bc44eef01a78f762ed3c7e.webm?t=1770646795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个广阔、开放的世界正等着你。面对烈日炎炎的酷夏和冰天雪地的严冬，确保您和您的子民不会缺衣少食。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《中世纪王朝》将以其独特的类型组合让您沉浸其中，为您带来终极的中世纪体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/00ac1639072624487513dd042dc2994b.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/911973723c63c6e6ea48673d42ae3770.poster.avif?t=1770646795\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/911973723c63c6e6ea48673d42ae3770.webm?t=1770646795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/c74d05f5d387adbd5f5aa1a15cd05aa4.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span>对抗四季： 确保您和您的子民不会挨饿或渴死。猎捕野生动物、种植作物或交易资源，以备万全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/a3c4e4bf8fe346137f270e6ae726f0c3.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span>一切尽在你手： 如果没有合适的工具——无论是打猎、砍树、收割还是建筑，您都将寸步难行。但千万小心磨损的问题，以免你的镐在荒郊野外无法使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/a32cd4d2710384b3d05f6d6dfb88e42f.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span>活到老，学到老： 在与NPC互动、照顾家人、探索郁郁葱葱的世界或为他人完成任务的过程中，发展自己的角色、专攻某项技能或成为真正的全才。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/584e60d90c291aefd10c3766001e40c1.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span>创建村庄： 您集城市规划者、建造者和看守者于一身！协调布局、管理居民、收集资源、生产商品并开展贸易，帮助社区繁荣壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/d3db92acbebb2519253cd8471fab7982.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/260893c31857dadadce1196d124b95ab.poster.avif?t=1770646795\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/260893c31857dadadce1196d124b95ab.webm?t=1770646795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>中世纪的世界具有极具挑战的危险和优美的环境，就在你触手可及之处！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/0eb3b2cf25818cebc8e7676af8338bf3.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/82fd244c03d8c7ed1b98152cfdd7b8f9.poster.avif?t=1770646795\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/82fd244c03d8c7ed1b98152cfdd7b8f9.webm?t=1770646795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/681edea68f5f9a9fb340856d2a187c87.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逼真的开放世界：</strong>在美丽的开放世界中探索两个广阔的地图：山谷（单人）和U型河道（单人与合作模式）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人合作模式：</strong>最多可与4位朋友组队，共同体验合作游戏的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色定制：</strong>通过详细的角色创建器个性化你的头像。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逼真的动态环境：</strong>沉浸在完整的四季循环中，体验动态的昼夜交替和逼真的天气，同时积极融入环境，从砍伐树木到探索洞穴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结构和内饰多样化：</strong> 创建超过25种不同类型的建筑，从简陋的棚屋到坚固的石屋，并选择120多种家具和装饰件来个性化它们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的手工制作：</strong>制作300多种物品，包括武器、工具、家具和服装。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与野生动物互动：</strong> 与狼、野猪、鹿、野牛以及更多栖息在森林中的野生动物邂逅。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存机制：</strong>监测你的食物、水、健康和体力水平。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能树：</strong>通过购买新技能来提升你的角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特事件：</strong>体验对游戏有直接影响的动态事件和决定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务和经济：</strong>参与任务、贸易和经济活动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>社会动态和家庭建设：</strong>与 NPC 建立联系，建立自己的家庭，发展关系，从而在游戏中享受为人父母的喜悦，并有机会将自己的传承延续下去。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>广阔的景观会随着您的行动而不断变化，这一切都让您万分着迷。砍伐树木、收集资源或探索神秘洞穴：</strong> 所到之处均有新发现。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/6b0abaf727f981397694f0def2ac765d.webp?t=1770646795\" width=610 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/987db44996893bbb66618354e4e25935.poster.avif?t=1770646795\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129580/extras/987db44996893bbb66618354e4e25935.webm?t=1770646795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
